tags.description: Atlantic City Electric Owns All the Electric Transmission Lines from this line southward. However it doesn't operate the Oyster Creek Substation that is by JCPL along with the area around Vineland NJ, all 500KV Lines in its territory are owned by PSEG.

Appears to be another 230/69kv line Needs Verification.

I didn't check this line at all just looked the poles closet the substation in Manahawkin/Long Beach Island.

The 230kv line continues along these structures however reviewing the line going into the station here the other poles non 230kv have 6 disc insulators which can be seen off W Bay Ave which calculates to 69KV. Recent street view images help plotting this.
